name: Stanford Open Credit Project
body:
### Mission
The mission of Stanford Open Credit Project (SOCP) is to accelerate the dissemination of open credit data and technologies in order to understand and prevent credit crises.

### Members
Kay Giesecke, Stanford University, giesecke@stanford.edu (co-Chair)
Kapil Jain, Stanford University, kkjain@stanford.edu (co-Chair)

### Open Source Technology
http://github.com/stanford-ocp

### Contributors
Please email us to inquire about membership or contributing to SOCP.

### Sponsors
We appreciate the generous support of: the Stanford Center for Financial and Risk Analytics (CFRA), the Stanford Institute for Computational and Mathematical Engineering (ICME)
